pbmeta:ControlKit.Description: Sequel II DNA Internal Control Complex 3.2 contains a fixed template of 11 kb length, bound to Sequel DNA Polymerase 2.2 for use as an internal sequencing control on the Sequel System. Reagent quantities provide spike-in controls for a minimum of 24 samples.
pbmeta:ControlKit.Name: Sequel II DNA Internal Control Complex 3.2

pbmeta:TemplatePrepKit.Description: The SMRTbell Prep Kit contains reagent supplies to perform SMRTbell library preparations of primer-annealed SMRTbell libraries for insert sizes ranging from 500 bp to over 20 kb.
pbmeta:TemplatePrepKit.Name: SMRTbell Prep Kit 3.0

pbmeta:BindingKit.Description: he Sequel II Binding Kit 3.2 contains reagent supplies to bind prepared DNA template libraries to the Sequel II Polymerase 2.2 in preparation for HiFi sequencing. The result is a DNA polymerase template complex ready for use with Adaptive Loading on the Sequel II and Sequel IIe Systems. Sequel II Polymerase 2.2 should be used with Sequel II Sequencing Kit 2.0. Reagent quantities support at least 24 binding reactions, and at least 3 SMRT Cells 8M per reaction (72 cells total), depending on use case, sample size and concentration. Note: Sequel II Binding Kit 3.2 is not recommended for inserts smaller than 3 kb
pbmeta:BindingKit.Name: Sequel II Binding Kit 3.2

pbmeta:SequencingKitPlate.Description: The DNA Sequencing Kit contains a sequencing reagent plate with chemistry for single molecule real-time sequencing on the PacBio Sequel Dev with Dynamic Loading. Reagent quantities support 4 sequencing reactions to be used in conjunction with SMRT Cell 4Pac(s). (4 Cells max/Each Row supplies reagents for 1 Sequel SMRT Cell)
pbmeta:SequencingKitPlate.Name: Sequel II Sequencing Plate 2.0 (4 rxn)
